Renowned aviation designer Burt Rutan created the Voyager and GlobalFlyer, aiming to break records.
Steve Fossett's solo, non-stop flight around the world faces challenges from the unpredictable jet stream.
The lightweight aircraft showcases Rutan's innovations and fuel efficiency advancements.
With Virgin seeking spotters for the GlobalFlyer, Fossett embarks on a daring journey, overcoming equipment issues.
The flight tests his endurance and skills, with hopes of inspiring future aircraft designs.
Rutan's legacy shines through as Fossett navigates the globe, aiming for aviation history with a pioneering spirit.
